BRUSSELS -- France is ready to take part in a "new military
structure" in NATO, the country's top military officer said
Tuesday after taking part in its first meeting of the alliance's
military committee for 30 years.
</P>
<P>
MONTEVIDEO -- Paraguayan General Lino Oviedo Tuesday dropped
his rebellious attitude toward the government of President Juan
Carlos Wasmosy, saying he will obey the president's decision to
remove him from the post of the army commander.
</P>
