<P>
According to latest reports, General Oviedo has finally dropped
his rebellious attitude and agreed to obey the president's order.
</P>
<P>
Oviedo said in a tape recording disseminated by the army's
Communications Office that he will hand over his post to General
Oscar Diaz Delmas today.
</P>
<P>
In turn, Oviedo will become the new defense minister.
</P>
<P>
