<HEADLINE> Croatia, China to Cooperate in Bosnia's Reconstruction </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZAGREB, April 23 (Xinhua) -- Economic and trade officials from
China and Croatia agreed today to cooperate in the reconstruction
of the war-torn Bosnia and former Yugoslavia.
