<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The Paraguayan congress
today called for defense of the constitution in face of the
rebellion by the country's Army Commander.
</P>
<P>
The congress in a communique called for citizens, political
parties and mass organizations to demonstrate in Asuncion, the
capital of Paraguay, and in other cities.
</P>
<P>
