<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, April 23 (Xinhua) -- It is Russia's constant foreign
policy priority to maintain and develop a long, stable, friendly
and mutually beneficial relationship with China, a Russian Foreign
Ministry spokesman said today.
</P>
